5. Termination
This Agreement is effective until terminated. The Agreement will terminate automatically without notice from financechest if the Licensee fails to comply with any provision contained herein. Upon termination, the Licensee must destroy all copies of the Product and all of its component parts.

6. Consequences of Non-Compliance
